## 6. 钩子配置

### 命令钩子

```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "SessionStart": [{
      "matcher": "*",
      "hooks": [{
        "type": "command",
        "command": "echo 'Claude Code 启动'",
        "statusMessage": "初始化环境..."
      }]
    }],
    "PreToolUse": [{
      "matcher": "Write",
      "hooks": [{
        "type": "command",
        "command": "git add .",
        "async": true
      }]
    }],
    "PostToolUse": [{
      "matcher": "Edit",
      "hooks": [{
        "type": "command",
        "command": "prettier --write {{file_path}}",
        "timeout": 5000
      }]
    }]
  }
}
```

### LLM 提示钩子

```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "PreToolUse": [{
      "matcher": "Bash",
      "hooks": [{
        "type": "prompt",
        "prompt": "检查这个命令是否安全：$ARGUMENTS",
        "model": "claude-haiku-4-5"
      }]
    }]
  }
}
```

### Agent 验证钩子

```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "PostToolUse": [{
      "matcher": "Bash(npm test*)",
      "hooks": [{
        "type": "agent",
        "prompt": "验证测试是否全部通过：$ARGUMENTS",
        "timeout": 60000
      }]
    }]
  }
}
```

### HTTP 钩子

```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "SessionStart": [{
      "matcher": "*",
      "hooks": [{
        "type": "http",
        "url": "https://your-webhook.com/notify",
        "headers": {
          "Authorization": "Bearer $API_TOKEN",
          "Content-Type": "application/json"
        },
        "allowedEnvVars": ["API_TOKEN"]
      }]
    }]
  }
}
```

### 可用钩子事件

- `PreToolUse` - 工具使用前
- `PostToolUse` - 工具使用后
- `PostToolUseFailure` - 工具失败后
- `SessionStart` - 会话开始
- `SessionEnd` - 会话结束
- `UserPromptSubmit` - 用户提交提示
- `WorktreeCreate` - 创建工作树
- `WorktreeRemove` - 删除工作树
- `TaskCompleted` - 任务完成
- `ConfigChange` - 配置变更

